# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# |<----  Sử dụng tối đa 50 ký tự  ---->|

# Body: Giải thích chi tiết (optional)
# |<----   Tối đa 72 ký tự mỗi dòng   ---->|

# Footer: Issue references (optional)
# Example: Closes #123, Refs #456

# --- COMMIT TYPES ---
# feat:     Tính năng mới
# fix:      Sửa bug
# docs:     Thay đổi documentation
# style:    Format code (không ảnh hưởng logic)
# refactor: Refactor code
# perf:     Cải thiện performance
# test:     Thêm/sửa tests
# chore:    Build process, dependencies
# ui:       UI/UX updates
# config:   Configuration changes

# --- SCOPES (Examples) ---
# worker:   Worker-related features
# farmer:   Farmer-related features
# admin:    Admin-related features
# auth:     Authentication
# api:      API integration
# ui:       UI components
# layout:   Layout components
# db:       Database changes
# global:   Global changes

# --- EXAMPLES ---
# feat(worker): add job search filter by distance
# fix(farmer): resolve payment calculation error
# ui(admin): update dashboard chart colors
# docs(readme): add installation instructions
# refactor(auth): simplify login logic
